snippet.textDisplay: Well, I think we need to consider the meaning of composition first. Composition is an action of putting things together; formation or construction. Which in case of music means putting together the lyrics, meter, rhythm, vocals and instruments to come out with something called as a song. So if u r saying that this combination is exactly same as that of Arifa and Shabnam, you are perhaps right. Otherwise it is perfectly alright to say that "THIS" particular piece has been composed by Ram Sampath.
